Quote: SOUTHERN KINGFISH ... <i>Other names: Jordanidia solandri</i>; kingfish, hake, barraconda; king barracouta,  Tasmanian kingfish (Australia); tikati (Maori). SOUTHERN KINGFISH <i>Jordanidia solandri </i> This is the King Barracouta of Australia and the so-called Hake of more southern New Zealand waters.
